  "title": "Investment Banking Audit Manager / Senior Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>APAC coverage</li><li>Good learning curve</li><li>Opportunity for career growth</li></ul><p>A Banking client is seeking an <strong>Investment Banking Audit Manager / Senior Manager </strong> to join the team.In this role, you will lead APAC Audits for the Investment Banking domain - end-to-end audit execution including planning, controls testing, drafting reports and follow ups. There will be travel required to regional branches for audit visits and you will be able to have face time with senior business stakeholders to evaluate internal controls, developing recommendations for them to improve any work processes.</p><p>The ideal candidate should have at least 5-8 years relevant experience within audit for a within Investment Banking/Financial Markets Audit, preferably with solid understanding of capital markets/front office/trading activities. A Finance or Business university graduate with CPA certification preferred. Strong communication skills and stakeholder management skills a pre-requisite for the role.</p><p>If you are keen, please click on the link to apply or email me with your updated CV at Rachel.ljy@ethosbc.com. Look forward to hearing back, thank you.<br /></p><p>Reg. No. R1987809<br />BeathChapman Pte Ltd<br />Licence no. 16S8112</p>",
